    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "The project will promote and finance commercial agribusiness enterprises collective owned by small farmers (collective enterprises) and individual small enterprises (individual enterprises) through Small Farmers Development Bank (SFDB), an apex development bank owned by Small Farmers Agriculture Cooperatives (SFACs). SFDB provides wholesale loans to SFACs; then SFACs re-lend to their small farmer members. Under the project, SFACs will re-lend the loan proceeds to their members' collective enterprises and individual enterprises."
      },
